###############################################
### GET ALL PRODUCTS (with optional filters)
###############################################

### Get all products (no filters)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products

### Get all products with pagination (page 1, 2 items per page)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?page=1&limit=2

### Get all electronics
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?category=electronics

### Get all clothing
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?category=clothing

### Get products priced between $50 and $500
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?minPrice=50&maxPrice=500

### Get products with minimum price of $200
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?minPrice=200

### Get electronics sorted by price (low to high)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?category=electronics&sortBy=price_asc

### Get all products sorted by price (high to low)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?sortBy=price_desc

### Complex query: get electronics between $50-$1000, sorted by price ascending, page 1 with 5 items
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?category=electronics&minPrice=50&maxPrice=1000&sortBy=price_asc&page=1&limit=5

